thread.title: TV | The Bourne Supremacy

author: Brian Lloyd
title: TV | The Bourne Supremacy
text: The follow-up to The Bourne Identity and Paul Greengrass' first time out with Matt Damon, The Bourne Supremacy took the gritty action of the first one and infused with a documentary-style sensibility. Bourne and his partner, Marie (Franka Potente) are now on the run in India when he is unwittingly framed for the murder of several CIA agents and documents that detail stolen money that financed a Russian oligarch. Arguably the best of the entire series.
